function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	
tTarget = Hydra.ActorsInGroup(Group_TargetAiToggle)

for i, idMonster in ipairs(tTarget) do	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idMonster) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idMonster, false) 
		Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idMonster, true)
		Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idMonster, false)
		--Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_Bark_1, idMonster) --<this is broken
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(CONV_Bark_1, idActor, idMonster)
		
		--wait for convo to finish then reset monster to proper ai and targetability.
		Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(CONV_Bark_1)	
		--Hydra.TraceScreen("I did the thing")
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idMonster, true) 
		Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idMonster, false)
		Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idMonster, true)
	end
end



end

end
